  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1257058638" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1257058638" />
    <a title="Daren" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11995655-daren"><img alt="Daren" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1347678806p2/11995655.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1257058638?book_show_action=true">Jan 31, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Daren" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Daren" href="/user/show/11995655-daren">Daren</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780146000133" href="/book/show/381033.Sonny_s_Blues">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11995655-daren?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11995655-daren?shelf=fiction-short-story-ies">fiction-short-story-ies</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11995655-daren?shelf=usa">usa</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11995655-daren?shelf=4-star">4-star</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11995655-daren?shelf=usa-author">usa-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11995655-daren?shelf=p60s">p60s</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11995655-daren?shelf=excerpt">excerpt</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1257058638" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12860111778913376529">Three short stories about life in Harlem for young black children. Other reviewers have pointed to the 1950&apos;s which seems right with situations described - eg mention of horse and cart deliveries, motor cars, the evolved state of jazz (&quot;Like Louis Armstrong?&quot;... &quot;No. I&apos;m not talking about none of that old-time, down-home crap.&quot;)<br/><br/>These are not happy memory stories, they are hard times. Themes include disconnection (and reconnection) of family, drugs, jazz, parental relationship / control of childr</span>
  <span id="freeText12860111778913376529" style="display:none">Three short stories about life in Harlem for young black children. Other reviewers have pointed to the 1950's which seems right with situations described - eg mention of horse and cart deliveries, motor cars, the evolved state of jazz ("Like Louis Armstrong?"... "No. I'm not talking about none of that old-time, down-home crap.")<br /><br />These are not happy memory stories, they are hard times. Themes include disconnection (and reconnection) of family, drugs, jazz, parental relationship / control of children, societal disconnection.<br /><br />Well written, realistic and atmospheric - great description in these short, easy to read stories.<br /><br />Four stars.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12860111778913376529" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


