        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3931624292" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10692454755495825384">This story is about pain, suffering, deception and the healing power of art.<br/>Not any pain, though. It’s the pain of the opressed, their impotence and the violence they are subjected to. <br/>Nevertheless there is always a slit in this circular and asfixiating reality: art, creation, particularly, music. Through the voices, their melodies and rythms, another world is created where the words do not reach. <br/>Beautifully written, it is music in words.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


