        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1917365027" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17440443660272726097">Wow. What an outstanding talent. This novella was not only incredibly well written, with a magnetic rhythm into it, it also touched me deeply. This was the best short novel I&apos;ve read and I definitely need to read more (or everything) by Baldwin. <br/><br/>It&apos;s better to step into it blindly so I will only say one more thing: please read this!</span>
  <span id="freeText17440443660272726097" style="display:none">Wow. What an outstanding talent. This novella was not only incredibly well written, with a magnetic rhythm into it, it also touched me deeply. This was the best short novel I've read and I definitely need to read more (or everything) by Baldwin. <br /><br />It's better to step into it blindly so I will only say one more thing: please read this!</span>
